OL,3,CSouth Tyneside bin strikes to be cut
OL,4,Cshort after discussions with unions
OL,6,FBin strikes in South Tyneside will be
OL,7,Fcut short following "positive
OL,8,Fdiscussions" between the council and
OL,9,FUnions.
OL,11,FThe GMB Union has agreed that members
OL,12,Fof its waste crew will return to work
OL,13,Fon Tuesday 7 May.
OL,15,FAction short of strike will be
OL,16,Fsuspended to allow an action plan,
OL,17,Fwhich was agreed in April following
OL,18,Ffeedback from the workforce and
OL,19,FUnions, to take effect.
