OL,3,CSouth Tyneside bin strikes to be cut
OL,4,Cshort after discussions with unions
OL,6,FThe action plan will see changes
OL,7,Fintroduced such as more investment in
OL,8,Fbalancing bin rounds, upgrading
OL,9,Fequipment and communication and
OL,10,Fbehaviour protocols being put in place.
OL,12,FStuart Wright, Director of Place and
OL,13,FCommunities at South Tyneside Council
OL,14,Fsaid: "I am glad that we have been
OL,15,Fable to agree a way forward that not
OL,16,Fonly cuts the current period of strike
OL,17,Faction short, but that ends action
OL,18,Fshort of strike and ensures that we
OL,19,Fhave that much needed period of
OL,20,Fstability we've been looking for.
