OL,3,CSouth Tyneside bin strikes to be cut
OL,4,Cshort after discussions with unions
OL,6,F"We have gone to great lengths to
OL,7,Fengage with and listen to the concerns
OL,8,Fof our workforce.
OL,10,F"The action plan gives all parties a
OL,11,Fconstructive way forward and we will
OL,12,Fnow press ahead to deliver it. We need
OL,13,Feveryone on board to bring about the
OL,14,Fimprovements to the service and
OL,15,Fworking conditions that the workforce
OL,16,Fhas asked for.
OL,18,F"I'd like to once again thank the
OL,19,Fpeople of South Tyneside for their
OL,20,Fpatience in what has been a
OL,21,Fchallenging period for the borough."
