OL,3,CSouth Tyneside bin strikes to be cut
OL,4,Cshort after discussions with unions
OL,6,FThe news has also been welcomed by
OL,7,FSouth Shields MP Emma Lewell-Buck.
OL,9,FBin crews began industrial action in
OL,10,FNovember 2023, with a GMB re-ballot
OL,11,Fproviding the potential for action to
OL,12,Fcontinue for a further six months.
OL,14,FMark Wilson, GMB Organiser said: "I am
OL,15,Fpleased that we have come to an
OL,16,Fagreement that helps us deliver the
OL,17,Fagreed plan and gives us the
OL,18,Ffoundations to move forward positively.
