OL,3,CSouth Tyneside bin strikes to be cut
OL,4,Cshort after discussions with unions
OL,6,F"We are hopeful that we will be in a
OL,7,Fposition to bring industrial action to
OL,8,Fan end following a period of
OL,9,Fstability, engagement, and investment
OL,10,Fin the service.
OL,12,F"All parties appreciate the level of
OL,13,Fdisruption caused to the people of
OL,14,FSouth Tyneside over the last six
OL,15,Fmonths but today we have agreed the
OL,16,Ffoundations to bring an end to that in
OL,17,Fthe longer term."
